{"tid":783073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「Captain Nancy」如果粒石真係喺家燕媽媽到","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:58:23.000Z","uid":29348,"like":75,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"278b8c6d800d38d1036c0f9956c37aee592fd764","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/173043_3df080eee5fdb3075cf031a21157982e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F173043_3df080eee5fdb3075cf031a21157982e.png&h=5b563399&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e42e746aafabaea686e1805330f1243c0a9217fa","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"「Captain Nancy」如果粒石真係喺家燕媽媽到<br />\n<br />\n時間：復仇者聯盟3後<br />\n<br />\n「shit⋯⋯粒石係強國貨嚟。」魁隆看著已嚴重損毀的無限手套說。<br />\n<br />\n宇宙間本已被消滅的一半人口，在魁隆以為大業已成後全部復活過來。<br />\n<br />\n「唔怪得老闆你出完大招隻手套就爆炸啦，咁我地宜家點算好？」嘰嘰兵說。<br />\n<br />\n「心靈寶石，既然幻視額頭上果粒係假嘢，真果粒一定仲喺地球。」被作弄的魁隆再次發動起無限寶石的力量。<br />\n<br />\n「𠵱，老闆，隻手套唔係廢左架啦咩？」嘰嘰兵又說。<br />\n<br />\n「廢左我被雷神劈果陣點走呀？」損毀的無限手套還能發動有限的力量，被雷神劈仲嚴重過俾雷劈。<br />\n<br />\n綠光在魁隆手中閃現，那是源自時間寶石的光芒。<br />\n<br />\n「只要逆轉時間，搶番真果粒心靈寶石，就無人可以再阻止我拯救世界！」魁隆雄心壯志，為了完成這畢生志願他不惜推自己養女落街。<br />\n<br />\n「老闆你知真果粒石係邊？宜家好多嘢都made in china架啵。」嘰嘰兵擔心老闆又再中伏。<br />\n<br />\n「係某人嘅額頭上面。」<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"43230d5b536dc20022f1531c996882f81b64fac1","tid":783073,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577b4a044faed91184d20c773616536b7ea5b527","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"地球，池力共鎮<br />\n<br />\n「Nancy，we need your help.」神盾局局長，單眼佬找上了家燕媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n「唉呀！我都唔知你講乜？」剛娶完新抱正享受著天倫之樂的她，無想到和平的日子快要終結。<br />\n<br />\n「we know you keep the stone.」單眼佬指向自己光滑的額頭。<br />\n<br />\n「不如你講番廣東話啦！」家燕媽媽別過臉說。<br />\n<br />\n「粒石，喺你粒墨到。」單眼佬在化成塵土前想求助的其實不是captain marvel ，他只是看錯了N為M。<br />\n<br />\n時間被逆轉到魁隆進入瓦干達搶奪幻視額上的無限寶石前，所以單眼佬立即趕來池力共鎮。<br />\n<br />\n「Nancy, please.」單眼佬懇切哀求。<br />\n<br />\n「我⋯⋯我無做呢啲嘢好耐㗎啦！」家燕媽媽耍手擰頭。<br />\n<br />\n「We need your team，The Mother Studio.」除了Marvel Studio外的，另一股勢力。<br />\n<br />\n巨輪戰艦從天而降，單眼佬知道的事情，魁隆同樣知道，要集齊六顆無限寶石，魁隆也終於來到池力共鎮。<br />\n<br />\n「搵額頭上有粒墨嘅人出嚟，其他格殺勿論。」對於魁隆的理念來說，犧牲一少撮人是在所難免。<br />\n<br />\n但對於皆大歡喜的家燕媽媽來說，這是不能唏呀唏呀唏就算的事。<br />\n<br />\n嘰嘰大軍開始大肆破壞，漫步在市中心的魁隆無視人命，只要一揮動無限手套，數百條生命就此消逝，以時間寶石逆轉過後，無限手套重現閃爍金光。<br />\n<br />\n「嘰嘰！唔係𠵱個！呢粒只係普通嘅墨！」嘰嘰兵的長矛快要貫穿平民之際，強而有力的手從後把他扔上半空。<br />\n<br />\n「你哋要搵嘅人，係我。」換上一身寶石胄甲，紅色的披風隨風飄揚，家燕媽媽化身Captain Nancy，為池力共鎮的人民再披起戰衣。<br />\n<br />\n「終於嚟啦⋯⋯我嘅心靈寶石。」魁隆闊步前行，以力量之石的力量把人群分隔兩邊。<br />\n<br />\n心靈寶石的主人終於對上無限之戰的最終頭目。"},{"pid":"ea60644b02f1606e255dac9d8bc5e3e532bc9089","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"「交粒墨⋯⋯唔係！交粒石出嚟！」藍光閃耀，魁隆把Captain Nancy吸引去他身邊。<br />\n<br />\n「唔得～𠵱粒係我象徵嚟架。」Captain Nancy在虛空中猛力踏步，十字火光衝破了魁隆的力量。<br />\n<br />\n魁隆躍起想追上半空中的Captain Nancy，但只見Captain Nancy繼續向上飛馳。<br />\n<br />\n「隕石墮落！我要將你連同池力共鎮一齊消滅！」藍色光芒閃得更耀眼，魁隆想以空間寶石的力量把宇宙隕石也拉到地面。<br />\n<br />\n無數隕石向地面墮落，但見Captain Nancy無懼這攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n「十字步！」Captain Nancy衝向最大的一顆隕石，雙腳踏上高速舞動，十字型的巨大力量把巨石瞬間粉碎。<br />\n<br />\n「十字步！十字步！十字步！十字步！」<br />\nCaptain Nancy在長空中不斷瞬移，以十字步擊破空中大大小小的隕石。<br />\n<br />\n「嘰嘰！」大量飛行嘰嘰兵撲向Captain Nancy，但橙色的閃光把他們全部掃清。<br />\n<br />\n「Nancy⋯⋯」單眼佬看著橙色的光芒欣喜地笑。<br />\n<br />\n「大家一齊跳十字舞咪幾好囉。」心靈寶石在Captain Nancy額上顯現，強大的力量令魁隆也目定口呆。<br />\n<br />\n「只有毀滅一半人口，宇宙先會得到平衡！」紫色力量爆發，魁隆向Captain Nancy打出強力衝擊波。<br />\n<br />\n「團結一心就有新轉機㗎啦。」Captain Nancy額上寶石射出橙色光線，光線和衝擊波互相抵消。<br />\n<br />\n「就好似你個下爬咁，搽多啲cream自然會好㗎啦。」Captain Nancy從天而降，她和魁隆的對決才剛開始。<br />\n<br />\n「我有千軍萬馬，你額上嘅墨⋯⋯唔係！係石，我一定要搶到手！」魁隆還不甘示弱。<br />\n<br />\n「邊個話⋯⋯Mother Studio，得我一個㗎？」但Captain Nancy胸有成竹，因為她的隊友即將來到。<br />\n<br />\n「Captain Nancy」Maybe continue⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9434b3e16e9866416b39bf48445dfe34daab0283","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"43230d5b536dc20022f1531c996882f81b64fac1","tid":783073,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae1404ebb5cff47aba281bfd4ec7d7d38360321","tid":783073,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7859f95e5ebeef8922d4d7788f9de9dc5bfc04","tid":783073,"uid":178800,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"好無聊，唔想討論家燕媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b9548606f58fc4f83abb08a367899c8bb06be6","tid":783073,"uid":37650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlm G持"},{"pid":"77717e08931465f226a5708c47d30399c91d3e29","tid":783073,"uid":172514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"長故？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b19f66defe61b282106ab013fb2346c7a16d4d","tid":783073,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"睇晒<br />\n請繼續"},{"pid":"e823a633b4d2a5ae77a9a2c901353a2ecfaeec11","tid":783073,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.karousell.com/media/photos/products/2018/06/12/_____1528744535_ee3f4665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.karousell.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fproducts%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F_____1528744535_ee3f4665.jpg&h=3a925d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解會有嘰嘰兵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72c011048c78073f056068d3b13e9149a6e4528","tid":783073,"uid":6041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"TVBUniverse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c730b81f7ce413b11abc7392fd536e0150f8e4d","tid":783073,"uid":117894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:36:18.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecf83a72837a311795b77a4b7dcfbd4dc484739","tid":783073,"uid":29348,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"今日見到張poster好搞笑，諗住寫黎大家笑下咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8765b23e0223e0dd2beb42c8e4e9642e5f6d5d","tid":783073,"uid":198711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"是咪會繼續寫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw妖氣2幾時出姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635ca1733adf6dead2c653f061efd0fa27b8749e","tid":783073,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a8765b23e0223e0dd2beb42c8e4e9642e5f6d5d","tid":783073,"uid":198711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"是咪會繼續寫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma